@laanwj OT - see this for problems with resizing:
![peers](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1419649/3160488/78644b4a-eb21-11e3-8043-e8b414c7f18b.png)

We only use that resizefixer in receivecoins and transactionsview, perhaps it doesn't work well with the peers layout, which has an element right to the table!?

